# --- Bundled into the client (VITE_*) ---

# Optional: absolute API origin without trailing slash. Required for GitHub Pages (set as
# repo variable VITE_API_URL in CI). Leave unset for same-origin (HF Docker, local stack).
#
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-live-api.example.com

# Public path for the app (must end with / unless "/"). GitHub Pages project site:
# VITE_BASE=/your-repo-name/

# --- Dev server only (read by Vite, not embedded in the app) ---

# Where `npm run dev` proxies API traffic. Default below if unset.
# VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8000
